            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FZ5DKIYTT%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FZ5DKIYTT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22document%22%2C%22note%22%3A%22Citation%20Key%3A%20oab_go_consulta_2019%5Cnpublisher-place%3A%20Goi%C3%A2nia%5Cntex.urldate%3A%20YYYY-MM-DD%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22Consulta%20n%C2%BA%20201901668%22%2C%22URL%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oabgo.org.br%2Farquivos%2Fdownloads%2Fvoto-consulta-201901668-1513115.pdf%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22literal%22%3A%22ORDEM%20DOS%20ADVOGADOS%20DO%20BRASIL%20%E2%80%93%20SE%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20Goi%C3%A1s%22%7D%5D%2C%22issued%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222019%22%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22oab_go_consulta_2019%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(22/10/2025, 19:51:39)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F5HWD9JW7%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22SQQCCPNS%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B170.18%2C490.467%2C538.638%2C502.264%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C475.467%2C538.554%2C487.264%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C460.467%2C538.779%2C472.264%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C445.587%2C538.568%2C457.384%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C430.587%2C538.817%2C442.384%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C415.707%2C538.668%2C427.504%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C400.707%2C538.68%2C412.504%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C385.807%2C538.627%2C397.604%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C370.807%2C538.854%2C382.604%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C355.807%2C538.75%2C367.604%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C340.927%2C538.675%2C352.724%5D%2C%5B170.18%2C325.927%2C209.807%2C337.724%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FZ5DKIYTT%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201c\u201cPrezados, boa tarde! Gostaria de orienta\u00e7\u00e3o sobre a seguinte situa\u00e7\u00e3o: Se o advogado \u00e9 contratado por Maria, para propor a\u00e7\u00e3o de alimentos e execu\u00e7\u00e3o. Maria, mais tarde, dispensa o advogado e n\u00e3o lhe paga o que fora acordado, embora ele j\u00e1 tenha protocolado a inicial. Fato seguinte, Jo\u00e3o, que \u00e9 pai de Maria, quer lhe contratar o mesmo advogado, que antes defendia os interesses da filha na A\u00e7\u00e3o de alimentos e execu\u00e7\u00e3o, para agora defende-lo na continuidade da a\u00e7\u00e3o de execu\u00e7\u00e3o, uma vez que a a\u00e7\u00e3o de alimentos j\u00e1 fora arquivada. A d\u00favida \u00e9: Mesmo Maria tendo contratado Jo\u00e3o e assinado contrato, e logo depois ela o dispensa, ele pode, agora, atuar no mesmo processo s\u00f3 que defendendo os interesses de pai de Maria\u201d\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FZ5DKIYTT%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">ORDEM DOS ADVOGADOS DO BRASIL \u2013 SE\u00e7\u00e3o Goi\u00e1s, 2019, p. 1</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
            "node_type": "note"
