            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22The%20judicialization%20of%20healthcare%20access%20in%20Brazil%20raises%20debates%20on%20enforcing%20the%20right%20to%20health%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20public%20policies.%20This%20article%20conducts%20a%20systematic%20review%20in%20the%20CAPES%20database%2C%20analyzing%20107%20articles%20on%20the%20topic.%20The%20results%20indicate%20growing%20academic%20interest%2C%20with%2010%20identified%20subthemes%20ranging%20from%20drug%20provision%20to%20constitutional%20issues.%20Judicialization%20ensures%20rights%20but%20poses%20challenges%20to%20healthcare%20system%20management.%20It%20is%20concluded%20that%20balancing%20individual%20demands%20with%20sector%20sustainability%20is%20essential.%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22Revista%20de%20Direito%22%2C%22DOI%22%3A%2210.32361%2F2025170221490%22%2C%22ISSN%22%3A%222527-0389%2C%201806-8790%22%2C%22issue%22%3A%2202%22%2C%22journalAbbreviation%22%3A%22RD%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22pt%22%2C%22license%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby-nc%2F4.0%22%2C%22page%22%3A%2201-25%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22DOI.org%20(Crossref)%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22A%20judicializa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20do%20acesso%20%C3%A0%20sa%C3%BAde%3A%20perspectivas%20e%20an%C3%A1lises%20em%20uma%20revis%C3%A3o%20de%20literatura%22%2C%22title-short%22%3A%22A%20judicializa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20do%20acesso%20%C3%A0%20sa%C3%BAde%22%2C%22URL%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fperiodicos.ufv.br%2Frevistadir%2Farticle%2Fview%2F21490%22%2C%22volume%22%3A%2217%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Lopes%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Eliana%20De%20Jesus%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Vasconcelos%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22H%C3%A9lio%20Victtor%20Rodrigues%20De%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Carneiro%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Maria%20Samanta%20Menezes%22%7D%5D%2C%22accessed%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222025%22%2C10%2C28%5D%5D%7D%2C%22issued%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222025%22%2C9%2C3%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22lopesJudicializacaoAcessoSaude2025%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(28/10/2025, 09:15:46)</h1>\n<p><img data-attachment-key=\"ZA2EUBC9\" width=\"744\" height=\"812\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FK5ANIHDJ%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22AP86M6GY%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%228%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A7%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B75.156%2C285.713%2C521.406%2C772.588%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%228%22%7D%7D\"/><br/><span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%228%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Lopes et al., 2025, p. 8</span>)</span></p><p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FK5ANIHDJ%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%225REM49TM%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2211%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A10%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B194.48%2C446.446%2C509.492%2C459.852%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C425.746%2C509.652%2C439.152%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C405.046%2C509.556%2C418.452%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C384.346%2C509.628%2C397.752%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C363.646%2C509.796%2C377.052%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C342.946%2C509.304%2C356.352%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C322.246%2C509.64%2C335.652%5D%2C%5B85.2%2C301.546%2C439.56%2C314.952%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2211%22%7D%7D\">\u201ca crescente judicializa\u00e7\u00e3o do acesso \u00e0 sa\u00fade tem impacto direto sobre a gest\u00e3o do SUS e a efici\u00eancia or\u00e7ament\u00e1ria, influenciando a forma como os recursos s\u00e3o distribu\u00eddos. Estudos apontam que o aumento das demandas judiciais tem levado ao deslocamento de verbas originalmente planejadas para pol\u00edticas p\u00fablicas amplas, o que pode comprometer a equidade na presta\u00e7\u00e3o dos servi\u00e7os de sa\u00fade (Brasil, 2021). Isso refor\u00e7a a necessidade de mecanismos mais eficazes de concilia\u00e7\u00e3o entre a prote\u00e7\u00e3o do direito individual e a sustentabilidade do sistema p\u00fablico de sa\u00fade.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2211%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Lopes et al., 2025, p. 11</span>)</span></p><p><img data-attachment-key=\"3FLI4J48\" width=\"718\" height=\"385\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FK5ANIHDJ%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22C2EUUXPQ%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B82.031%2C280.129%2C512.656%2C510.754%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D\"/><br/><span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F7C9JS3QZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Lopes et al., 2025, p. 12</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
