            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FGZ32KLXI%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FGZ32KLXI%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22A%20coopera%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20no%20Novo%20CPC%3A%20da%20armadilha%20%C3%A0%20%C3%A9tica.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Nogueira%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22M%C3%A1rcio%20Melo%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Vidal%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22C%C3%A1ssio%20Esteves%20Jaques%22%7D%5D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22nogueiraCooperacaoNoNovo%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br>(20/11/2025, 04:32:11)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FTP23DCE3%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22HWA878UV%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B141.206%2C574.831%2C521.36%2C581.309%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C553.951%2C520.944%2C560.429%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C533.072%2C521.366%2C539.549%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C512.192%2C520.929%2C518.67%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C491.313%2C521.576%2C497.79%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C470.433%2C520.882%2C476.911%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C449.553%2C521.163%2C456.031%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C428.674%2C521.55%2C435.152%5D%2C%5B92.967%2C407.794%2C344.399%2C414.272%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FGZ32KLXI%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201cResumo: O presente trabalho tem por finalidade a prec\u00edpua an\u00e1lise da norma contida no art. 6o da Lei n. 13.105/2015, prestes a irradiar efeitos no processo civil brasileiro. Considerando que a voga da referida Lei foi trazer a prometida efetividade da tutela jurisdicional pela Constitui\u00e7\u00e3o Federal sem alijar os r\u00e9us em geral de suas garantias consagradas na hist\u00f3ria dos direitos fundamentais, a coopera\u00e7\u00e3o pode ser valor \u00fatil, mas arriscado se manejado com finalidade de ressuscitar figuras cuja presen\u00e7a \u00e9 repulsada pela sistem\u00e1tica da Novel Lei Adjetiva Civil. Positiv\u00e1 la na Lei \u00e9 tema controverso na abalizada doutrina, eis que a interpreta\u00e7\u00e3o desse art. 6o demanda, como todo o ordenamento jur\u00eddico posto, a filtragem hermen\u00eautico constitucional devida.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FGZ32KLXI%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Nogueira e Vidal, p. 1</span>)</span> Este trabalho tem relev\u00e2ncia j\u00e1 que expressa as discuss\u00f5es sobre a cl\u00e1usula arbitral logo no in\u00edcio da aplica\u00e7\u00e3o da vig\u00eancia do CPC de 2015. O que pode ajudar a fixar o marco inicial da an\u00e1lise da varia\u00e7\u00e3o das disputas e evolu\u00e7\u00f5es doutrin\u00e1rias e de jurisprud\u00eancia ao longo dos anos que se passariam a partir do estudo.</p>\n</div></div>",
