            "Abstract Note",
            "Objective: the purpose of this paper is to analyze some aspects of the action to set aside arbitral award and understand them to avoid the filing of annulment lawsuits that may undermine the arbitration. Method: by the research in the specialized doctrine and in the Federal District Court\u2019s case law database, there were selected rulings that address important themes to understand this action. Result: the conclusion reached is that the Federal District Court has examined various aspects of the action to set aside arbitral award and their decisions are in total consonance with the specialized doctrine."
