            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FIHHL3JVV%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FIHHL3JVV%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22The%20understanding%20and%20application%20of%20the%20law%20suffered%2C%20over%20time%2C%20significant%20changes.%20The%20ideas%20post-positivistic%20spread%20by%20the%20legal%20order%2C%20inspiring%20the%20movement%20neoprocessualista%20(phase%20of%20the%20variant%20formalism)%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20a%20process%20geared%20to%20the%20achievement%20of%20justice%2C%20respect%20for%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20guarantees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20principles%2C%20among%20which%20we%20highlight%20the%20cooperation.%20Thus%2C%20within%20the%20new%20system%2C%20the%20form%20by%20itself%20not%20more%20justified.%20Therefore%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20new%20directions%20taken%20by%20the%20contemporary%20civil%20process%2C%20the%20research%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20principle%20of%20cooperation%2C%20closely%20linked%20to%20the%20movement%20neoprocessualista%2C%20and%20how%2C%20from%20it%2C%20if%20structure%20the%20model%20of%20cooperative%20process%2C%20as%20well%20what%20the%20repercussions%20that%20fundamental%20law%20of%20the%20process%20launches%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20arbitration.%20The%20theme%20is%20presented%20through%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20literature%20and%20legislation.%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22pt%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22Zotero%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22O%20PRINC%C3%8DPIO%20DA%20COOPERA%C3%87%C3%83O%20COMO%20NORMA%20FUNDAMENTAL%20DO%20PROCESSO%20CIVIL%20E%20SEUS%20REFLEXOS%20NA%20ARBITRAGEM%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Neves%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Fabiana%20Junqueira%20Tamaoki%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Isogai%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Stephanie%20Karoline%20Maioli%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Godoy%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Sandro%20Marcos%22%7D%5D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22nevesPRINCIPIOCOOPERACAOCOMO%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 03:26:03)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FJ67UFX2E%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22FD8CEGTP%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B85.104%2C328.178%2C538.558%2C339.086%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C314.378%2C538.574%2C325.286%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C300.578%2C538.63%2C311.486%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C286.778%2C538.606%2C297.686%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FIHHL3JVV%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201cRESUMO: A compreens\u00e3o e aplica\u00e7\u00e3o do Direito sofreu, ao longo do tempo, significativas mudan\u00e7as. As ideias p\u00f3s-positivistas se espalharam pelo ordenamento jur\u00eddico, inspirando o movimento neoprocessualista (fase do formalismo-valorativo), voltado a um processo orientado \u00e0 realiza\u00e7\u00e3o da justi\u00e7a, respeitador dos direitos e garantias fundamentais, bem como\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FIHHL3JVV%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Neves et al., p. 1</span>)</span></p><p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FJ67UFX2E%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22TET4M9CI%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%222%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A1%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B85.104%2C743.428%2C538.442%2C754.336%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C729.628%2C538.488%2C740.536%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C715.828%2C538.61%2C726.736%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C702.028%2C538.5%2C712.936%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C688.228%2C538.512%2C699.136%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C674.428%2C538.66%2C685.336%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C660.628%2C137.28%2C671.536%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C646.828%2C538.792%2C657.736%5D%2C%5B85.104%2C633.028%2C203.592%2C643.936%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FIHHL3JVV%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%222%22%7D%7D\">\u201cdos princ\u00edpios, dentre os quais destaca-se o da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o. Assim, dentro da nova sistem\u00e1tica, a forma pela forma n\u00e3o mais se justificaria. Portanto, ciente dos novos rumos tomados pelo processo civil contempor\u00e2neo, a pesquisa visa abordar o princ\u00edpio da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o, intimamente ligado ao movimento neoprocessualista, e como, a partir dele, se estrutura o modelo de processo cooperativo, bem como quais os reflexos tal norma fundamental do processo lan\u00e7a no meio arbitral de solu\u00e7\u00e3o de conflitos. O tema \u00e9 apresentado atrav\u00e9s das an\u00e1lises bibliogr\u00e1fica e legislativa. PALAVRAS-CHAVE: Neoprocessualismo. C\u00f3digo de Processo Civil. Princ\u00edpio da Coopera\u00e7\u00e3o. Arbitragem\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FIHHL3JVV%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%222%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Neves et al., p. 2</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
