            "item_type": "note",
            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F8SMY9FWF%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F8SMY9FWF%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22The%20dissertation%20seeks%20to%20establish%20the%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20foundations%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20cooperation%20in%20civil%20procedure%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20an%20implicit%20constitutional%20principle%20deriving%20from%20the%20principle%20of%20solidarity%20(art.%203.%C2%BA%2C%20I%2C%20Constitution%20of%20the%20Federative%20Republic%20of%20Brazil%20-%20CFRB)%2C%20access%20to%20justice%20(art.%205.%C2%BA%2C%20XXXV%20%2C%20CFRB)%2C%20due%20process%20of%20law%20(art.%205%C2%BA%2C%20LIV%20%2C%20CFRB)%2C%20adversary%20system%20(art.%205.%C2%BA%2C%20LV%20%2C%20CF%2F1988)%20and%20reasonable%20duration%20of%20proceedings%20(art.%205.%C2%BA%20%2C%20LXXVIII%20%2C%20CF%2F1988)%20.%20The%20essay%20seeks%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20principle%20of%20cooperation%20is%20the%20basic%20idea%20of%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Civil%20Procedure%20(CPC)%20of%201973%20and%20of%20the%20Project%20of%20the%20New%20CPC%2C%20including%20the%20art.%20339%20of%20CPC%2F1973%20and%20those%20that%20discipline%20the%20disclosure%20of%20documents%20and%20things.%20The%20dissertation%20seeks%20to%20establish%20the%20limits%20to%20the%20principle%20of%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Brazilian%20legal%20system%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20(art.%205.%20%C2%BA%20%2C%20X%2C%20CF%2F1988)%20and%20the%20right%20to%20remain%20silent%20(art.%205.%C2%BA%20%2C%20LXIII%20%2C%20CF%20%2F%201988).%20At%20last%2C%20the%20dissertation%20seeks%20to%20establish%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20cooperation%20and%20the%20way%20it%20operates%20in%20civil%20procedure.%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22pt%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22Zotero%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22O%20PRINC%C3%8DPIO%20DA%20COOPERA%C3%87%C3%83O%20E%20A%20EXIBI%C3%87%C3%83O%20DE%20DOCUMENTO%20OU%20COISA%20NO%20PROCESSO%20CIVIL%20(SEGUNDA%20PARTE)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Queiroz%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Pedro%20Gomes%22%2C%22non-dropping-particle%22%3A%22de%22%7D%5D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22dequeirozPRINCIPIOCOOPERACAOEXIBICAO%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 03:29:49)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FHHZJA4QU%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22FRN42HKL%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221761%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B56.664%2C428.668%2C362.604%2C439.576%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C414.868%2C362.724%2C425.776%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C401.068%2C362.896%2C411.976%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C387.238%2C362.592%2C398.146%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C373.438%2C362.794%2C384.358%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C359.638%2C362.776%2C370.546%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C345.838%2C362.582%2C356.746%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C332.038%2C362.896%2C342.946%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C318.238%2C362.58%2C329.146%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C304.438%2C363.016%2C315.346%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C290.638%2C362.654%2C301.546%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C276.838%2C362.592%2C287.746%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C263.018%2C362.484%2C273.926%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C249.218%2C362.896%2C260.126%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F8SMY9FWF%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221761%22%7D%7D\">\u201cResumo: A disserta\u00e7\u00e3o procura estabelecer os fundamentos constitucionais e legais do princ\u00edpio da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o no processo civil, descrevendo-o como um princ\u00edpio constitucional impl\u00edcito, decorrente do princ\u00edpio da solidariedade (art. 3o, I, CF/1988), da isonomia (art. 5.o, caput, CF/1988), do acesso \u00e0 ordem jur\u00eddica justa (art. 5.o, XXXV, CF/1988), do devido processo legal (art. 5.o, LIV, CF/1988), do contradit\u00f3rio, da ampla defesa (art. 5.o, LV, CF/1988) e da dura\u00e7\u00e3o razo\u00e1vel do processo (art. 5.o, LXXVIII, CF/1988). O trabalho procura demonstrar que o princ\u00edpio da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 a ideia base de v\u00e1rios dispositivos do C\u00f3digo de Processo Civil (CPC) de 1973 e do Projeto do Novo CPC, entre eles o art. 339 do CPC/1973 e aqueles que disciplinam a exibi\u00e7\u00e3o de documento ou coisa. A disserta\u00e7\u00e3o procura estabelecer os limites do princ\u00edpio da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o exis\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F8SMY9FWF%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221761%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Queiroz, p. 1761</span>)</span></p><p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FHHZJA4QU%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%225MYVZG95%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221762%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A1%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B56.664%2C525.268%2C362.734%2C536.176%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C511.468%2C362.58%2C522.376%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C497.668%2C362.592%2C508.576%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C483.868%2C362.532%2C494.776%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C470.068%2C170.52%2C480.976%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C442.468%2C362.896%2C453.376%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C428.668%2C362.896%2C439.576%5D%2C%5B56.664%2C414.868%2C176.844%2C425.776%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F8SMY9FWF%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221762%22%7D%7D\">\u201ctentes no ordenamento jur\u00eddico brasileiro, em especial o direito \u00e0 privacidade (art. 5.o, X, CF/1988) e o direito ao sil\u00eancio (art. 5.o, LXIII, CF/1988). Enfim, a disserta\u00e7\u00e3o procura estabelecer o conte\u00fado do princ\u00edpio da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o e a forma como este opera no processo civil. Palavras-chave: Princ\u00edpio da coopera\u00e7\u00e3o. Exibi\u00e7\u00e3o de documento ou coisa. Contradit\u00f3rio participativo. Direito \u00e0 privacidade. Direito ao sil\u00eancio.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F8SMY9FWF%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221762%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Queiroz, p. 1762</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
