            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FXD5RL8CI%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FXD5RL8CI%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22The%20article%20deals%20with%20connected%20contracts%20in%20the%20strict%20sense%20and%20with%20networked%20contracts%2C%20both%20included%20in%20the%20category%20of%20connected%20contracts%20in%20the%20broad%20sense%2C%20with%20the%20general%20objective%20of%20pointing%20out%20the%20most%20common%20legal%20implications%20regarding%20such%20contracts.%20Its%20specific%20objectives%20are%20(a)%20to%20define%20the%20contratual%20coalition%20and%20connection%3B%20(b)%20to%20clarify%20the%20hypotheses%20of%20the%20abuse%20of%20rights%20in%20connected%20contracts%3B%20and%20(c)%20to%20elucidate%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Judiciary%20in%20cases%20where%20there%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20objective%20good%20faith%20in%20the%20establishment%20of%20contractual%20connections.%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22Revista%20Brasileira%20de%20Direito%20Civil%20em%20Perspectiva%22%2C%22DOI%22%3A%2210.26668%2FIndexLawJournals%2F2526-0243%2F2023.v9i1.9507%22%2C%22ISSN%22%3A%222526-0243%2C%202526-0243%22%2C%22issue%22%3A%221%22%2C%22journalAbbreviation%22%3A%22RBDC%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22pt%22%2C%22license%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby-nc-nd%2F4.0%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22DOI.org%20(Crossref)%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22O%20RECONHECIMENTO%20DOS%20CONTRATOS%20CONEXOS%20NO%20CASO%20CONCRETO%3A%20A%20PROTE%C3%87%C3%83O%20DOS%20DIREITOS%20HUMANOS%20NOS%20NEG%C3%93CIOS%20JUR%C3%8DDICOS%22%2C%22title-short%22%3A%22O%20RECONHECIMENTO%20DOS%20CONTRATOS%20CONEXOS%20NO%20CASO%20CONCRETO%22%2C%22URL%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Findexlaw.org%2Findex.php%2Fdireitocivil%2Farticle%2Fview%2F9507%22%2C%22volume%22%3A%229%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Santos%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Paulo%20Junior%20Trindade%20%20Dos%22%7D%5D%2C%22accessed%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222025%22%2C11%2C20%5D%5D%7D%2C%22issued%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222023%22%2C8%2C1%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22santosRECONHECIMENTODOSCONTRATOS2023%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 03:30:40)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FQAFARPBI%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22YT92KQD6%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B56.64%2C646.309%2C103.897%2C655.203%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C635.029%2C538.39%2C644.082%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C623.509%2C538.19%2C632.562%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C611.989%2C538.633%2C621.042%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C600.469%2C537.818%2C609.522%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C589.069%2C455.601%2C598.122%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C577.279%2C153.697%2C586.173%5D%2C%5B56.64%2C565.999%2C358.156%2C575.052%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FXD5RL8CI%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201cRESUMO: O artigo trata dos contratos conexos em sentido estrito e dos contratos em rede, ambos englobados pela categoria dos contratos conexos em sentido amplo, tendo como objetivo geral apontar as implica\u00e7\u00f5es jur\u00eddicas mais comuns no que tange a tais contratos. Seus objetivos espec\u00edficos s\u00e3o (a) definir a coliga\u00e7\u00e3o e a conex\u00e3o contratuais; (b) esclarecer as hip\u00f3teses de configura\u00e7\u00e3o do abuso de direito nos contratos conexos; e (c) elucidar o papel do Poder Judici\u00e1rio nos casos em que se verifica a viola\u00e7\u00e3o da boa-f\u00e9 objetiva no estabelecimento das conex\u00f5es contratuais. PALAVRAS-CHAVE: Abuso de direito. Contratos at\u00edpicos. Contratos conexos. Direitos humanos.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FXD5RL8CI%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Santos, 2023, p. 1</span>)</span> Este trabalho pode se revelar de import\u00e2ncia impar, j\u00e1 que explora a ideia de contratos em rede em rela\u00e7\u00e3o a defesa de direitos humanos, o que traz a discuss\u00e3o para a esfera constitucional.</p>\n</div></div>",
