            "item_type": "note",
            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FKDKDWUEE%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FKDKDWUEE%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22This%20article%20addresses%20the%20business%20model%20of%20the%20so-called%20sharing%20economy%20and%20its%20legal%20impacts%2C%20notably%20with%20regard%20to%20safeguarding%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20involved%20parties%2C%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20possible%20disparities%20between%20users%20of%20the%20sharing%20platforms.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20this%20study%20analyzes%20the%20possibility%20of%20using%20remedies%20designed%20for%20the%20contractual%20protection%20of%20consumers%20in%20order%20to%20solve%20problems%20arising%20from%20such%20relations%2C%20provided%20that%20they%20are%20systematically%20coherent%20and%20appropriate%20to%20the%20axiology%20of%20the%20legal%20order%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20concrete%20interests%20of%20the%20parties%20in%20sharing%20economy%20contracts.%20As%20an%20exemplary%20application%2C%20this%20study%20will%20address%20some%20problems%20related%20to%20the%20validity%20of%20clauses%20in%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20use%20stipulated%20by%20sharing%20platforms.%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22Pensar%20-%20Revista%20de%20Ci%C3%AAncias%20Jur%C3%ADdicas%22%2C%22DOI%22%3A%2210.5020%2F2317-2150.2018.10834%22%2C%22ISSN%22%3A%222317-2150%2C%201519-8464%22%2C%22issue%22%3A%223%22%2C%22journalAbbreviation%22%3A%22Pensar%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22pt%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22DOI.org%20(Crossref)%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22Tutela%20da%20vulnerabilidade%20contratual%20nas%20rela%C3%A7%C3%B5es%20de%20economia%20do%20compartilhamento%22%2C%22URL%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fojs.unifor.br%2Frpen%2Farticle%2Fview%2F10834%22%2C%22volume%22%3A%2225%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Souza%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Eduardo%20Nunes%20De%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Rodrigues%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22C%C3%A1ssio%20Monteiro%22%7D%5D%2C%22accessed%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222025%22%2C11%2C20%5D%5D%7D%2C%22issued%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222020%22%2C9%2C21%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22souzaTutelaVulnerabilidadeContratual2020%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 02:44:01)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FDIXCAGE7%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22I4ZYETA3%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B68.032%2C573.421%2C544.248%2C581.772%5D%2C%5B68.041%2C561.424%2C544.254%2C569.775%5D%2C%5B68.041%2C549.427%2C544.244%2C557.778%5D%2C%5B68.041%2C537.43%2C544.245%2C545.781%5D%2C%5B68.032%2C525.421%2C544.447%2C533.772%5D%2C%5B68.032%2C513.421%2C544.464%2C521.772%5D%2C%5B68.032%2C501.421%2C456.706%2C509.772%5D%2C%5B68.032%2C484.451%2C543.899%2C492.803%5D%2C%5B68.032%2C473.151%2C125.056%2C481.503%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FKDKDWUEE%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201cO presente artigo aborda o modelo negocial da economia compartilhada (tamb\u00e9m chamado de sharing economy) e seus impactos jur\u00eddicos, notadamente no tocante \u00e0 tutela da vulnerabilidade das partes envolvidas, em aten\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e0s poss\u00edveis disparidades existentes entre os usu\u00e1rios das plataformas de compartilhamento. Para isso, analisa-se a possibilidade de utiliza\u00e7\u00e3o dos rem\u00e9dios da tutela contratual do consumidor para solucionar problemas oriundos dessas rela\u00e7\u00f5es, desde que sistematicamente coerentes e adequados \u00e0 axiologia do ordenamento e aos interesses concretos de contratantes na economia compartilhada. Como hip\u00f3tese particular de aplica\u00e7\u00e3o, o estudo abordar\u00e1 alguns problemas relativos \u00e0 validade de disposi\u00e7\u00f5es dos termos e condi\u00e7\u00f5es de uso estipuladas por plataformas de compartilhamento. Palavras-chave: Economia compartilhada. Vulnerabilidade. Direito do consumidor. Contratos de ades\u00e3o. Direito civilconstitucional.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FKDKDWUEE%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Souza e Rodrigues, 2020, p. 1</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
