            "item_type": "note",
            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FI66Z4L3L%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FI66Z4L3L%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22article-journal%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22This%20study%20aims%20to%20understand%20the%20perspectives%20of%20the%20business%20relationship%20developed%20between%20social%20media%20providers%20and%20their%20users%2C%20weighing%20the%20essentiality%20of%20the%20service%20against%20the%20consideration%20provided%20by%20the%20consumer%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20surveillance%20capitalism%20and%20the%20legal%20recognition%20of%20existential%20contracts.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20the%20study%20was%20developed%20using%20the%20inductive%20method%2C%20through%20specific%20observations%20of%20the%20social%2C%20political%2C%20and%20business%20context%20between%20the%20client%20and%20service%20provider%2C%20analyses%20of%20legal%20institutions%20and%20practical%20repercussions%2C%20especially%20regarding%20fundamental%20rights%3B%20as%20well%20as%20reasoning%20and%20the%20development%20of%20logical%20propositions%20based%20on%20the%20considerations%20developed.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20some%20relevant%20conclusions%20were%20reached%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20among%20them%3A%20(i)%20the%20processing%20of%20personal%20data%20by%20providers%2C%20to%20obtain%20indirect%20income%20from%20the%20service%20through%20the%20targeting%20of%20personalized%20advertising%2C%20when%20it%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20transfer%20of%20ownership%20of%20the%20data%20or%20uses%20that%20harm%20self-determination%2C%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20legal%20system%3B%20(ii)%20the%20indirect%20form%20of%20remuneration%20should%20constitute%20a%20subsidiary%20response%2C%20and%20the%20consumer%20should%20be%20offered%2C%20as%20a%20priority%2C%20the%20option%20of%20paying%20in%20cash%3B%20(iii)%20it%20is%20recommended%20that%20there%20be%20public%20policies%20to%20fund%20the%20use%20of%20social%20networks%20for%20those%20who%20cannot%20afford%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20service%2C%20given%20the%20importance%20of%20networks%20for%20promoting%20democracy%2C%20political%20pluralism%2C%20and%20other%20rights%20corollary%20to%20the%20individual%20and%20society.%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22pt%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22Zotero%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22VULNERABILIDADE%20DIGITAL%20DO%20CONSUMIDOR%20NOS%20MODELOS%20ZERO-%20PRICE%3A%20A%20(I)LEGALIDADE%20DA%20CESS%C3%83O%20IRRESTRITA%20DE%20DADOS%20PESSOAIS%20NOS%20TERMOS%20DE%20USO%20DAS%20REDES%20SOCIAIS%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Furtado%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Samuel%20Nunes%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Pinto%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Raissa%20Resende%22%7D%5D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22furtadoVULNERABILIDADEDIGITALCONSUMIDOR%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 05:21:45)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FMEFQDXSS%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22YBNBJJ9N%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%222%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B70.944%2C653.544%2C123.588%2C664.264%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C625.944%2C524.47%2C636.856%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C612.144%2C524.41%2C623.056%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C598.344%2C524.174%2C609.256%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C584.544%2C524.344%2C595.456%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C570.714%2C524.21%2C581.626%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C556.914%2C524.548%2C567.826%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C543.114%2C524.208%2C554.026%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C529.314%2C524.208%2C540.226%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C515.514%2C524.17%2C526.426%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C501.714%2C524.352%2C512.626%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C487.914%2C524.424%2C498.826%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C474.114%2C524.536%2C485.026%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C460.314%2C524.352%2C471.226%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C446.514%2C524.184%2C457.426%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C432.714%2C524.362%2C443.626%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C418.914%2C524.052%2C429.826%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C405.114%2C524.5%2C416.026%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C391.294%2C186.732%2C402.206%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C356.734%2C524.56%2C367.646%5D%2C%5B70.944%2C336.094%2C162.14%2C347.006%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FI66Z4L3L%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%222%22%7D%7D\">\u201cRESUMO Trata-se de trabalho que tem por objetivo entender as nuances da rela\u00e7\u00e3o negocial desenvolvida entre provedores de redes sociais e seus usu\u00e1rios, sopesando a essencialidade do servi\u00e7o \u00e0 contrapresta\u00e7\u00e3o fornecida pelo consumidor, no contexto do capitalismo de vigil\u00e2ncia e do reconhecimento jur\u00eddico de contratos existenciais. Para tanto, o desenvolvimento do trabalho deu-se mediante a utiliza\u00e7\u00e3o do m\u00e9todo indutivo, por meio de observa\u00e7\u00f5es espec\u00edficas sobre o contexto social, pol\u00edtico e negocial entre cliente e provedor de servi\u00e7os, an\u00e1lises de institutos jur\u00eddicos e repercuss\u00f5es pr\u00e1ticas, especialmente no que tange aos direitos fundamentais; al\u00e9m de racioc\u00ednios e levantamento de proposi\u00e7\u00f5es l\u00f3gicas a partir das considera\u00e7\u00f5es desenvolvidas. Ao fim, chegou-se a algumas conclus\u00f5es relevantes sobre o tema, dentre elas, as de que: (i) o tratamento de dados pessoais, realizado pelos provedores, para obten\u00e7\u00e3o de renda indireta pelo servi\u00e7o com direcionamento de propagandas personalizadas, quando n\u00e3o importe a transfer\u00eancia da propriedade dos dados ou usos que prejudiquem a autodetermina\u00e7\u00e3o encontra respaldo no ordenamento jur\u00eddico; (ii) a forma indireta de remunera\u00e7\u00e3o deve constituir resposta subsidi\u00e1ria, tendo de ser ofertado, ao consumidor, prioritariamente a op\u00e7\u00e3o para contrapresta\u00e7\u00e3o em dinheiro; (iii) \u00e9 recomend\u00e1vel que hajam pol\u00edticas p\u00fablicas para financiamento do uso das redes sociais \u00e0queles que n\u00e3o possuem condi\u00e7\u00f5es de pagar pelo servi\u00e7o, dada a relev\u00e2ncia das redes para a promo\u00e7\u00e3o da democracia, do pluralismo pol\u00edtico, e de outros direitos corol\u00e1rios ao indiv\u00edduo e \u00e0 sociedade. Palavras-chaves: Contratos existenciais; Dados pessoais; Redes sociais; Vulnerabilidade digital; Zero-Price.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FI66Z4L3L%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%222%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Furtado e Pinto, p. 2</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
