            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FM6WYS5J2%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FM6WYS5J2%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22legal_case%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22A%20discuss%C3%A3o%20jur%C3%ADdica%20sobre%20a%20extens%C3%A3o%20da%20responsabilidade%20do%20fiador%20em%20contratos%20de%20loca%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20predial%20urbana%20prorrogados%20por%20prazo%20indeterminado%2C%20bem%20como%20a%20aplica%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20de%20normas%20processuais%20e%20consumeristas%2C%20frequentemente%20gera%20controv%C3%A9rsia%20nos%20tribunais%20superiores.%20Este%20julgamento%20no%20Superior%20Tribunal%20de%20Justi%C3%A7a%20objetivou%20analisar%20os%20agravos%20internos%20interpostos%20e%20firmar%20o%20entendimento%20sobre%20a%20legitimidade%20passiva%20dos%20fiadores%20e%20a%20manuten%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20da%20fian%C3%A7a%2C%20al%C3%A9m%20de%20quest%C3%B5es%20processuais%20como%20a%20gratuidade%20de%20justi%C3%A7a.%20A%20pesquisa%20foi%20conduzida%20mediante%20a%20an%C3%A1lise%20de%20Agravo%20Interno%20e%20Recursos%20Especiais%2C%20utilizando%20o%20m%C3%A9todo%20de%20revis%C3%A3o%20de%20precedentes%20e%20a%20aplica%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20direta%20do%20Direito%20Civil%20e%20Processual%20Civil%2C%20com%20foco%20na%20Lei%20do%20Inquilinato%20(Lei%20n%C2%BA%208.245%2F91).%20Verificou-se%20a%20legitimidade%20passiva%20do%20fiador%20em%20demandas%20cumuladas%20de%20despejo%20e%20cobran%C3%A7a%20de%20alugu%C3%A9is%2C%20conforme%20o%20Art.%2062%20da%20Lei%208.245%2F91.%20Ademais%2C%20confirmou-se%20a%20inaplicabilidade%20do%20C%C3%B3digo%20de%20Defesa%20do%20Consumidor%20aos%20contratos%20de%20loca%C3%A7%C3%A3o.%20O%20principal%20achado%20reiterou%20a%20jurisprud%C3%AAncia%20pacificada%20do%20STJ%20de%20que%2C%20havendo%20cl%C3%A1usula%20contratual%20expressa%2C%20a%20fian%C3%A7a%20se%20prorroga%20automaticamente%20at%C3%A9%20a%20efetiva%20entrega%20das%20chaves%2C%20mesmo%20na%20prorroga%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20por%20prazo%20indeterminado.%20Concluiu-se%20pelo%20provimento%20do%20Agravo%20Interno%20para%20conhecer%20dos%20agravos%2C%20mas%20negou-se%20provimento%20aos%20Recursos%20Especiais%2C%20reafirmando%20a%20validade%20das%20cl%C3%A1usulas%20contratuais%20que%20estendem%20a%20responsabilidade%20do%20fiador%20e%20consolidando%20a%20seguran%C3%A7a%20jur%C3%ADdica%20no%20microssistema%20da%20loca%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20predial%20urbana.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20**Palavras-chave%3A**%20Loca%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20Predial%20Urbana.%20Fian%C3%A7a.%20Prorroga%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20Contratual.%20Superior%20Tribunal%20de%20Justi%C3%A7a.%20Lei%20do%20Inquilinato.%22%2C%22authority%22%3A%22QUARTA%20TURMA%20do%20Superior%20Tribunal%20de%20Justi%C3%A7a%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22MINISTRO%20RAUL%20ARA%C3%9AJO%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22AgInt%20nos%20EDcl%20no%20AI%20em%20Resp%20n%C2%BA%202227091%20-%20PR%20(2022%2F03208820)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Ara%C3%BAjo%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Raul%22%7D%5D%2C%22issued%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222023%22%2C9%2C25%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22araujoAgIntNosEDcl2023%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 13:49:37)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F93JYYPCC%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22ZX2KH4HY%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%22-%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B77%2C301.794%2C544.832%2C312.334%5D%2C%5B77%2C288.504%2C544.808%2C299.044%5D%2C%5B77%2C275.224%2C183.176%2C285.764%5D%2C%5B77%2C261.934%2C544.964%2C272.474%5D%2C%5B77%2C248.654%2C185.564%2C259.194%5D%2C%5B77%2C235.374%2C544.988%2C245.914%5D%2C%5B77%2C222.084%2C544.952%2C232.624%5D%2C%5B77%2C208.804%2C544.892%2C219.344%5D%2C%5B77%2C195.514%2C392.288%2C206.054%5D%2C%5B77%2C182.234%2C539.528%2C192.774%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FM6WYS5J2%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%22-%22%7D%7D\">\u201c2. Nos termos do art. 62, I e II, da Lei 8.245/91, o fiador \u00e9 parte leg\u00edtima para constar no polo passivo de demanda na qual se cumulam os pedidos de despejo e de cobran\u00e7a dos alugu\u00e9is e acess\u00f3rios da loca\u00e7\u00e3o. 3. N\u00e3o se aplica o C\u00f3digo de Defesa do Consumidor ao contrato de loca\u00e7\u00e3o regido pela Lei 8.245/91. Precedentes. 4. Nos termos da compreens\u00e3o pacificada do STJ, nos contratos de loca\u00e7\u00e3o predial urbana, \u00e0 luz do art. 39 da Lei do Inquilinato, d\u00e1-se a prorroga\u00e7\u00e3o da fian\u00e7a nos contratos locat\u00edcios prorrogados por prazo indeterminado, sem necessidade de anu\u00eancia do fiador, salvo expressa disposi\u00e7\u00e3o contratual em contr\u00e1rio. Incid\u00eancia da S\u00famula 83/STJ. 5. Agravo interno provido para conhecer dos agravos e negar provimento aos recursos especiais.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FM6WYS5J2%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%22-%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">Ara\u00fajo, 2023, pp. -</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
