            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FA5YLT9SQ%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FA5YLT9SQ%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22legal_case%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22A%20crescente%20relev%C3%A2ncia%20da%20arbitragem%20no%20Brasil%20imp%C3%B5e%20a%20necessidade%20de%20delimita%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20precisa%20dos%20sujeitos%20processuais%20em%20a%C3%A7%C3%B5es%20de%20controle%20judicial%2C%20notadamente%20as%20anulat%C3%B3rias%20de%20procedimento%20arbitral.%20Este%20trabalho%20objetivou%20analisar%20a%20natureza%20jur%C3%ADdica%20da%20c%C3%A2mara%20arbitral%20e%20determinar%20sua%20legitimidade%20para%20figurar%20no%20polo%20passivo%20de%20a%C3%A7%C3%B5es%20que%20visam%20a%20desconstitui%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20do%20processo.%20Trata-se%20de%20uma%20an%C3%A1lise%20jur%C3%ADdica%20e%20jurisprudencial%2C%20materializada%20no%20julgamento%20de%20Recurso%20Especial%20pelo%20Superior%20Tribunal%20de%20Justi%C3%A7a%20(STJ)%2C%20com%20interpreta%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20da%20Lei%20n%C2%BA%209.307%2F1996%20e%20do%20C%C3%B3digo%20de%20Processo%20Civil.%20O%20STJ%20estabeleceu%20que%20a%20institui%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20arbitral%2C%20por%20possuir%20natureza%20essencialmente%20administrativa%2C%20limita-se%20%C3%A0%20organiza%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20e%20apoio%20log%C3%ADstico%2C%20n%C3%A3o%20praticando%20atos%20jurisdicionais.%20Assim%2C%20constatou-se%20que%20a%20c%C3%A2mara%20arbitral%20n%C3%A3o%20det%C3%A9m%20interesse%20processual%20nem%20legitimidade%20para%20integrar%20o%20polo%20passivo%20da%20demanda%20anulat%C3%B3ria%2C%20devendo%20esta%20se%20restringir%20%C3%A0s%20partes%20que%20integraram%20o%20compromisso%20arbitral.%20Concluiu-se%20que%20o%20provimento%20do%20recurso%20especial%20refor%C3%A7a%20a%20distin%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20entre%20a%20fun%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20administrativa%20do%20%C3%B3rg%C3%A3o%20arbitral%20e%20a%20atividade%20decis%C3%B3ria%20dos%20%C3%A1rbitros%2C%20consolidando%20o%20entendimento%20de%20que%20a%20a%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20anulat%C3%B3ria%20deve%20espelhar%20a%20rela%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20jur%C3%ADdica%20material%20original.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20**Palavras-chave%3A**%20Arbitragem.%20Legitimidade%20Passiva.%20A%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20Anulat%C3%B3ria.%20C%C3%A2mara%20Arbitral.%20Recurso%20Especial.%22%2C%22authority%22%3A%22Terceira%20Turma%2C%20STJ%2C%20un%C3%A2nime%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22Ministro%20RICARDO%20VILLAS%20B%C3%94AS%20CUEVA%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22RE%20%201.433.940%20-%20MG%20(2014%2F0024753-9)%22%2C%22volume%22%3A%22DJe%2002%2F10%2F2017%22%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22RE1433940MG%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 13:54:53)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FGS2QXEIB%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22EL4ZRGIG%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B145.05%2C480.74%2C554.55%2C488.55%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C468.04%2C627.855%2C475.85%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C455.34%2C554.584%2C463.15%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C442.64%2C350.67%2C450.45%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C429.94%2C554.541%2C437.75%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C417.24%2C554.57%2C425.05%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C404.54%2C303.502%2C412.35%5D%2C%5B145.05%2C391.84%2C283.66%2C399.65%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FA5YLT9SQ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201cRECURSO ESPECIAL. A\u00c7\u00c3O ANULAT\u00d3RIA DE PROCEDIMENTO ARBITRAL. POLO PASSIVO. \u00d3RG\u00c3O ARBITRAL INSTITUCIONAL. C\u00c2MARA ARBITRAL. NATUREZA ESSENCIALMENTE ADMINISTRATIVA. ILEGITIMIDADE PASSIVA. INTERESSE PROCESSUAL. AUS\u00caNCIA. 1. A institui\u00e7\u00e3o arbitral, por ser simples administradora do procedimento arbitral, n\u00e3o possui interesse processual nem legitimidade para integrar o polo passivo da a\u00e7\u00e3o que busca a sua anula\u00e7\u00e3o. 2. Recurso especial provido.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FA5YLT9SQ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">\u201cRE 1.433.940 - MG (2014/0024753-9)\u201d, p. 1</span>)</span> Tribunais Arbitrais n\u00e3o s\u00e3o parte leg\u00edtima para figuar no polo passo de a\u00e7\u00f5es anulat\u00f3rias de compromisso arbitral.</p>\n</div></div>",
