            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FFLJ4TP55%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FFLJ4TP55%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22legal_case%22%2C%22abstract%22%3A%22A%20crescente%20utiliza%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20da%20arbitragem%20no%20Brasil%20levantou%20quest%C3%B5es%20processuais%20cruciais%20sobre%20a%20impugna%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20de%20decis%C3%B5es%20interlocut%C3%B3rias%20com%20car%C3%A1ter%20terminativo%2C%20notadamente%20a%20senten%C3%A7a%20arbitral%20parcial%2C%20cuja%20admissibilidade%20e%20regime%20recursal%20eram%20controversos%20antes%20da%20Lei%20n.%2013.129%2F2015.%20Este%20estudo%20objetivou%20definir%20o%20cabimento%20imediato%20da%20a%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20anulat%C3%B3ria%20prevista%20no%20Artigo%2033%20da%20Lei%20n.%209.307%2F1996%20contra%20a%20senten%C3%A7a%20arbitral%20parcial%2C%20em%20contraposi%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20ao%20entendimento%20de%20que%20a%20impugna%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20deveria%20aguardar%20a%20prola%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20da%20senten%C3%A7a%20final.%20A%20metodologia%20empregada%20consistiu%20na%20an%C3%A1lise%20hermen%C3%AAutica%20do%20sistema%20arbitral%20brasileiro%2C%20em%20harmonia%20com%20as%20reformas%20do%20C%C3%B3digo%20de%20Processo%20Civil%20de%201973%20(Lei%20n.%2011.232%2F2005)%20e%20com%20o%20suporte%20da%20doutrina%20especializada.%20Os%20resultados%20demonstraram%20a%20absoluta%20admissibilidade%20da%20senten%C3%A7a%20parcial%20no%20procedimento%20arbitral%2C%20compreendida%20como%20o%20ato%20que%20resolve%20definitivamente%20parte%20da%20causa%20(g%C3%AAnero%20do%20qual%20a%20senten%C3%A7a%20final%20%C3%A9%20esp%C3%A9cie)%2C%20sendo%20apta%20%C3%A0%20forma%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20da%20coisa%20julgada.%20Consequentemente%2C%20a%20a%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20anulat%C3%B3ria%20deve%20ser%20intentada%20de%20imediato%2C%20no%20prazo%20decadencial%20de%2090%20dias%2C%20sob%20pena%20de%20a%20quest%C3%A3o%20decidida%20tornar-se%20imut%C3%A1vel.%20Conclui-se%20que%20a%20possibilidade%20de%20impugna%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20imediata%20da%20senten%C3%A7a%20parcial%20arbitral%20%C3%A9%20inerente%20%C3%A0%20sua%20natureza%20e%20aos%20princ%C3%ADpios%20de%20celeridade%20e%20seguran%C3%A7a%20jur%C3%ADdica%20que%20regem%20a%20arbitragem%2C%20consolidando%20a%20autonomia%20do%20procedimento.%5Cn%5CnPalavras-chave%3A%20Arbitragem.%20Senten%C3%A7a%20Parcial.%20A%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20Anulat%C3%B3ria.%20Prazo%20Decadencial.%20Lei%209.307%2F96.%22%2C%22authority%22%3A%22Terceira%20Turma%20do%20STJ%2C%20por%20unanimidade%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22MINISTRO%20MARCO%20AUR%C3%89LIO%20BELLIZZE%22%2C%22note%22%3A%22RELAT%C3%93RIO%20E%20VOTO%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22REsp%20n%C2%BA%201.543.564%20-%20SP%20(2015%2F0171807-9)%22%2C%22URL%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stj.jus.br%2Fwebsecstj%2Fcgi%2Frevista%2FREJ.cgi%2FITA%3Fseq%3D1756850%26tipo%3D0%26nreg%3D201501718079%26dt%3D20181001%26formato%3DPDF%26salvar%3Dfalse%22%2C%22volume%22%3A%22DJe%3A%2001%2F10%2F2018%22%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22REspNo1543564%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 13:57:08)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2F6E5NZSPM%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%223M6WFYTX%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B89.2%2C560.24%2C555.208%2C568.05%5D%2C%5B89.2%2C547.24%2C555.224%2C555.05%5D%2C%5B89.2%2C534.24%2C555.725%2C542.05%5D%2C%5B89.2%2C521.24%2C555.162%2C529.05%5D%2C%5B89.2%2C508.24%2C555.162%2C516.05%5D%2C%5B89.2%2C495.24%2C555.433%2C503.05%5D%2C%5B89.2%2C482.24%2C516.69%2C490.05%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FFLJ4TP55%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D\">\u201cRECURSO ESPECIAL. MEDIDA CAUTELAR INOMINADA DESTINADA A ASSEGURAR O RESULTADO \u00daTIL DE A\u00c7\u00c3O ANULAT\u00d3RIA DE SENTEN\u00c7A PARCIAL ARBITRAL. 1. PROLA\u00c7\u00c3O DE SENTEN\u00c7A ARBITRAL PARCIAL. ADMISS\u00c3O, COM ESTEIO NA LEI N. 9.307/1996 (ANTES MESMO DAS ALTERA\u00c7\u00d5ES PROMOVIDAS PELA LEI N. 13.129/2015), NO C\u00d3DIGO DE PROCESSO CIVIL (COM REDA\u00c7\u00c3O DADA PELA LEI N. 11.232/2005). AJUIZAMENTO DE A\u00c7\u00c3O ANULAT\u00d3RIA, NO PRAZO DE 90 (NOVENTA) DIAS, NOS TERMOS DO ART. 33 DA LEI 9.307/1996. OBSERV\u00c2NCIA. 2. RECURSO ESPECIAL PROVIDO.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FFLJ4TP55%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">\u201cREsp n\u00ba 1.543.564 - SP (2015/0171807-9)\u201d, p. 1</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
